id-102690614%2Cimgsize-54228.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdeepika-padukones-comment-on-shah-rukh-khan-and-nayantharas-song-chaleya-sparks-rumours-that-she-also-has-a-dance-sequence-in-jawan%2Farticleshow%2F102689929.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102689929.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20makers%20of%20upcoming%20action%20thriller%20film%20'Jawan'%20have%20teased%20a%20new%20song%2C%20'Chaleya'%2C%20featuring%20Bollywood%20superstar%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20Nayanthara.%20The%20Hindi%20version%20of%20the%20romantic%20song%20will%20also%20have%20Tamil%20and%20Telugu%20versions.%20The%20Farah%20Khan-choreographed%20song%20is%20set%20to%20be%20released%20on%20August%2014.%20Fans%20and%20industry%20friends%20of%20SRK%20praised%20the%20teaser%2C%20with%20one%20user%20noting%20%26quot%3Bromance%20and%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20go%20hand%20in%20hand.%26quot%3B%20'Jawan'%20is%20set%20to%20release%20worldwide%20on%20September%207%2C%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22I%20Like%20To%20Captain%20How...%5C%22%3A%20Hardik%20Makes%20Honest%20Leadership%20Confession%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%200-2%20down%20in%20the%205-match%20T20I%20series%20against%20West%20Indies%2C%20Hardik%20Pandya's%20Indian%20team%20bounced%20back%20to%20win%20the%20next%20two%20matches%20in%20convincing%20fashion%2C%20making%20it%202-2%2C%20with%20just%20the%205th%20and%20the%20final%20match%20to%20go.%20After%20the%20West%20Indies%20leg%20of%20the%20series%2C%20both%20the%20teams%20arrived%20in%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%20where%20Shubman%20Gill%20and%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20stole%20th%20show%20with%20the%20bat.%20India%20skipper%20Hardik%20opened%20up%20on%20the%20dramatic%20turnaround%20in%20the%20team's%20fortunes%2C%20explaining%20his%20style%20of%20leadership.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Pandya%20it%20was%20just%20the%20beginning%20and%20urged%20the%20batters%20to%20be%20ready%20for%20bigger%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGill%20and%20Jaiswal%20were%20brilliant.%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20over%20their%20skillset.%20They%20just%20needed%20to%20spend%20some%20time%20between%20the%20wickets.%20Going%20forward%20we%20have%20to%20take%20more%20responsibility%20as%20a%20batting%20group%20and%20support%20the%20bowlers.%20I've%20always%20believed%20bowlers%20win%20matches%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pandya%20after%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20were%20trailing%200-2%20after%20the%20first%20two%20matches%2C%20but%20won%20the%20third%20and%20fourth%20games%20to%20roar%20back%20into%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandya%20was%20understandably%20elated%20by%20the%20team's%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20lost%20two%20games%20but%20in%20the%20first%20game%20it%20was%20our%20own%20errors.%20We%20were%20cruising%20and%20in%20the%20last%20four%20overs%20we%20slipped.%20We%20spoke%20about%20how%20these%20kinds%20of%20games%20show%20our%20character.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20boys%20took%20it%20(defeats)%20in%20their%20stride.%20The%20two%20games%20(after%20the%20first%20two%20defeats)%20we%20played%20reflected%20that%20we%20pulled%20up%20our%20socks%20and%20played%20some%20good%20cricket%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaiswal%2C%20who%20struck%20an%20unbeaten%2084%20off%2051%20balls%2C%20was%20adjudged%20man%20of%20the%20match%2C%20and%20the%20left-hander%20said%20he%20batted%20as%20per%20the%20team's%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWest%20Indies%20captain%20Rovman%20Powell%20said%20batsmen%20need%20to%20stick%20to%20their%20plans%20and%20play%20India%20spinners%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20stick%20to%20our%20plans.%20We%20always%20knew%20this%20series%20would%20come%20down%20to%20how%20we%20play%20against%20spinners%20(of%20India)%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Powell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691895360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fvodq748_hardik-pandya_650x300_07_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fi-like-to-captain-how-skipper-hardik-pandya-makes-honest-leadership-confession-4293627%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20nine-wicket%20win%20over%20West%20Indies%20in%20the%20fourth%20T20I%20left%20Hardik%20Pandya%20a%20pleased%20man.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fi-like-to-captain-how-skipper-hardik-pandya-makes-honest-leadership-confession-4293627%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fi-like-to-captain-how-skipper-hardik-pandya-makes-honest-leadership-confession-4293627%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fi-like-to-captain-how-skipper-hardik-pandya-makes-honest-leadership-confession-4293627%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kate%20Winslet's%20Iconic%20Overcoat%20From%20'Titanic'%20To%20Be%20Sold%20At%20Auction%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20overcoat%20worn%20by%20Hollywood%20actress%20Kate%20Winslet%20in%20the%20superhit%20movie%20'Titanic'%20is%20up%20for%20auction%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20fetch%20more%20than%20%24100%2C000%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F08%2F12%2Fkatie-winslets-titanic-overcoat-will-be-sold-at-auction%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20actress%20donned%20the%20floor-length%20overcoat%20in%20the%20sinking%20sequences%20of%20the%201997%20movie%2C%20including%20the%20scene%20when%20her%20character%20Rose%20frees%20Leonardo%20DiCaprio's%20character%20Jack%2C%20who%20was%20restrained%20to%20a%20pole%20on%20the%20flooded%20E-deck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKen%20Goldin%2C%20the%20Founder%20and%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20of%20the%20auction%20house%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgoldin.co%2Fitem%2Fkate-winslet-titanic-screen-worn-overcoatov6cq%3FqueryId%3DeyJxdWVyeUlkIjoiMTY3ZjM1N2QwMGQ3YTMzN2Y3Mjg1MWUwMzBiMzk4NjYiLCJjYXJkSW5kZXgiOjB9%5C%22%3EGoldin%20%3C%2Fa%3Estated%20that%20%26quot%3Bit's%20definitely%20a%20six-figure%20piece%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20go%20for%20%24100%2C000%20plus%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EPost%3C%2Fem%3E.%20As%20per%20the%20auctioneer%2C%20five%20individuals%20have%20already%20made%20offers%20as%20of%20Friday%20night%2C%20with%20the%20highest%20being%20%2434%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20coat%20still%20has%20water%20stains%20which%20occurred%20during%20the%20filming.%20Deborah%20Lynn%20Scott%2C%20who%20won%20the%20Oscar%20for%20Best%20Costume%20Design%20for%20her%20work%20on%20the%20James%20Cameron%20movie%2C%20created%20the%20pink%20wool%20overcoat%20with%20black%20embroidery.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20floor-length%20wool%20overcoat%20worn%20by%20Rose%20during%20those%20frantic%20moments%20as%20she%20navigates%20the%20sinking%20ship%20while%20rescuing%20Jack%20bears%20visible%20water%20stains%20on%20the%20inside%20and%20across%20the%20interior%20silk.%20Intricate%20embroidery%20in%20black%20appears%20alongside%20floral%20embroidery%20that%20gives%20the%20coat%20dynamic%20bespoke%20realism%20aligned%20with%20the%20fashion%20of%20the%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20auction%20house%20said%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20elaborate%20outfit%20is%20part%20of%20Goldin%20100%2C%20one%20of%20the%20auction%20house's%20most%20exclusive%20sales%2C%20with%20artefacts%20valued%20at%20%24100%2C000%20or