%20the%20Hawaiian%20island%20of%20Maui%2C%20she%20got%20no%20official%20warning%20and%20no%20order%20to%20evacuate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20know%20when%20we%20found%20that%20there%20was%20a%20fire%3F%20When%20it%20was%20across%20the%20street%20from%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2063-year-old%20told%20AFP%20in%20an%20evacuation%20center%20parking%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mountain%20behind%20us%20caught%20on%20fire%20and%20nobody%20told%20us%20jack.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReed%20herded%20her%20daughter%2C%20grandson%20and%20two%20pet%20cats%20into%20the%20car%20and%20careered%20out%20of%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20raced%20a%20line%20of%20fire%20to%20get%20my%20family%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cause%20of%20the%20terrifying%20inferno%20was%20still%20under%20investigation%20Saturday%2C%20but%20experts%20say%20that%20whatever%20sparked%20it%2C%20a%20collision%20of%20circumstances%20meant%20that%20it%20spread%20very%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20include%20the%20unchecked%20growth%20of%20flammable%20non-native%20plants%2C%20the%20volcanic%20topography%20that%20creates%20drying%20down-slope%20winds%2C%20an%20unusually%20parched%20winter%2C%20and%20a%20churning%20hurricane%20hundreds%20of%20miles%20(kilometers)%20to%20the%20southwest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20a%20state%20not%20unused%20to%20natural%20disasters%20--%20Hawaii%20has%20earthquakes%2C%20active%20volcanoes%2C%20a%20history%20of%20tsunamis%20and%20is%20regularly%20hit%20by%20powerful%20tropical%20storms%20--%20the%20lack%20of%20warning%20from%20authorities%20has%20puzzled%20and%20angered%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20underestimated%20the%20lethality%2C%20the%20quickness%20of%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20Hawaii%20congresswoman%20Jill%20Tokuda%20told%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20hurricane%20force%20winds%20are%20unknown%20to%20Hawaii%2C%20or%20dry%20brush%2C%20or%20red%20flag%20conditions.%20We%20saw%20this%20before%20in%20(Hurricane)%20Lane.%20We%20did%20not%20learn%20our%20lesson%20from%20Lane%20(in%202018)%20--%20that%20brush%20fires%20could%20erupt%20as%20a%20result%20of%20churning%20hurricane%20winds%20below%20us%20to%20the%20south%2C%26quot%3B%20Tokuda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20knocked%20out%20power%20and%20residents%20of%20Lahaina%20told%20reporters%20that%20they%20had%20no%20cell%20service%20--%20a%20common%20channel%20that%20authorities%20use%20when%20they%20want%20to%20alert%20residents%20to%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20electricity%20blackout%20would%20certainly%20have%20limited%20residents'%20ability%20to%20watch%20television%20or%20listen%20to%20the%20radio%20--%20two%20other%20channels%20where%20official%20warnings%20are%20issued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20more%20robust%20outdoor%20warning%20sirens%20that%20are%20intended%20to%20alert%20islanders%20to%20danger%20did%20not%20sound%2C%20the%20Hawaii%20Emergency%20Services%20Administration%20(HI-EMA)%20said%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeither%20Maui%20nor%20HI-EMA%20activated%20warning%20sirens%20on%20Maui%20during%20the%20wildfire%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20organization%20said%2C%20according%20to%20NBC%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHawaii's%20governor%2C%20Josh%20Green%2C%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Btoo%20early%20for%20me%20to%20tell%26quot%3B%20whether%20the%20absence%20of%20sirens%20was%20a%20technical%20failure%20or%20a%20deliberate%20decision%20by%20operators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20state's%20attorney%20general%2C%20Anne%20Lopez%2C%20said%20she%20was%20launching%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20timeline%20of%20the%20blaze%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bcritical%20decision-making%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20time%20the%20flames%20were%20spreading.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Big%20sirens'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Kamuela%20Kawaakoa%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20the%20town%20was%20left%20to%20fend%20for%20itself%20as%20disaster%20struck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20no%20emergency%20alerts.%20No%20warning%20systems%20went%20off%20--%20nothing%2C%20so%20some%20people%20didn't%20even%20know%20about%20the%20fire%20till%20it%20was%20too%20late%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2034-year%20old%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKawaakoa%2C%20who%20is%20now%20living%20in%20a%20pop-up%20tent%20and%20surviving%20on%20the%20kindness%20of%20strangers%2C%20said%20even%20without%20cell%20service%20and%20power%2C%20there%20should%20have%20been%20a%20way%20to%20tell%20people%20what%20was%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20still%20call%20911%20without%20any%20cell%20service%2C%20you%20should%20still%20be%20able%20to%20get%20emergency%20alerts%20on%20your%20phone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20we%20have%20these%20big%20sirens%20on%20poles...%20I'm%20sure%20they%20have%20a%20way%20of%20making%20it%20work%20even%20without%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20know%2C%20they%20gotta%20be%20prepared%20for%20that%20kind%20of%20stuff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKawaakoa%2C%20who%20worked%20in%20the%20now-razed%20Captain%20Jack's%20restaurant%20on%20Lahaina's%20touristy%20Front%20Street%2C%20said%20victims%20were%20pointing%20to%20downed%20power%20lines%20as%20a%20possible%20source%20of%20ignition%20for%20the%20blaze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%2C%20he%20wants%20to%20know%2C%20were%20they%20not%20shut%20off%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20there%20was%20more%20that%20could%20have%20been%20done%20to%20save%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20that%20died%20in%20this%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691894820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F6uv05b68_hawaii-victims_625x300_13_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnobody-told-us-jack-hawaii-wildfire-victims-as-death-count-touches-89-4293798%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20first%20Vilm