0nominee%20fall%20by%20the%20wayside%20amid%20his%20growing%20tangle%20of%20legal%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20first-time%20candidate%2C%20a%20father%20of%20two%20young%20children%2C%20has%20been%20rewarded%20with%20higher%20poll%20numbers%20than%20most%20of%20his%20more%20experienced%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Cultural%20cancer'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20political%20novice%20by%20any%20measure%2C%20Ramaswamy%20started%20his%20campaign%20with%20no%20national%20profile%20but%20has%20shocked%20primary%20watchers%20by%20rising%20to%20third%20in%20the%20Republican%20primary%20field%2C%20five%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20first%20vote%20in%20Iowa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20even%20snapping%20at%20the%20heels%20of%20Florida%20Governor%20Ron%20DeSantis%2C%20who%20is%20lagging%20around%2040%20points%20behind%20Trump%20but%20until%20recently%20looked%20relatively%20secure%20in%20the%20runner-up%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20ground%2C%20Ramaswamy%20has%20styled%20his%20politics%20on%20the%20agendas%20of%20the%20two%20men%20he%20hopes%20to%20usurp%2C%20making%20his%20stand%20against%20the%20%26quot%3Bwoke%26quot%3B%20ideology%20of%20the%20American%20left%20his%20signature%20policy%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20national%20identity%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%20darkly%2C%20accusing%20the%20country's%20elites%20of%20metastasizing%20a%20%26quot%3Bcultural%20cancer%26quot%3B%20--%20particularly%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20LGBTQ%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20message%20has%20found%20an%20appreciative%20audience%2C%20and%20his%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BWoke%2C%20Inc.%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20which%20he%20develops%20this%20thesis%2C%20is%20currently%20near%20the%20top%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20list%20of%20bestselling%20nonfiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBurning%20coal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20increasingly%20crowded%20field%20--%2017%20candidates%20have%20declared%20so%20far%20--%20Ramaswamy%20has%20been%20able%20to%20grab%20attention%20and%20headlines%20with%20a%20policy%20program%20that%20might%20be%20dismissed%20as%20too%20radical%20were%20his%20polling%20numbers%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vegetarian%20pianist%20wants%20to%20raise%20the%20voting%20age%20to%2025%20and%20lay%20off%2090%20percent%20of%20the%20staff%20at%20the%20US%20central%20bank%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20his%20ready-made%20solution%20for%20reviving%20growth%20in%20the%20United%20States%3F%20Burning%20coal%20%26quot%3Bunapologetically.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20he%20faces%20a%20steep%20uphill%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20all%20the%20other%20candidates%2C%20Ramaswamy's%20only%20chance%20is%20if%20Trump%20collapses%2C%26quot%3B%20political%20scientist%20Kyle%20Kondik%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20unusual%20for%20Republican%20presidential%20candidates%20to%20pull%20their%20punches%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20always%20managed%20to%20retain%20the%20loyalty%20of%20at%20least%20a%20third%20of%20the%20party%20regardless%20of%20the%20prevailing%20political%20winds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Ramaswamy%20has%20bumped%20the%20deference%20up%20a%20level%2C%20turning%20up%20at%20the%20courthouses%20in%20Miami%20and%20the%20capital%20Washington%20where%20Trump%20was%20appearing%20with%20pledges%20to%20pardon%20the%2077-year-old%20ex-president%20and%20demands%20that%20his%20rivals%20follow%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20fought%20a%20revolution%20in%20this%20country%2C%20in%201776%2C%20for%20a%20simple%20idea%20that%20we%20the%20people%20determine%20how%20we%20select%20our%20leaders%20and%20have%20a%20government%20that%20is%20accountable%20to%20its%20people%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20other%20way%20around%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20video%20filmed%20this%20month%20outside%20Washington's%20federal%20court%20complex.%