%20scarred%20by%20the%20flames%20but%20still%20stands%20upright%2C%20its%20branches%20denuded%20of%20green%20and%20its%20sooty%20trunk%20transformed%20into%20an%20awkward%20skeleton.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Underestimated%20the%20lethality'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHawaii's%20Attorney%20General%20Anne%20Lopez%20said%20her%20office%20would%20examine%20%26quot%3Bcritical%20decision-making%20and%20standing%20policies%20leading%20up%20to%2C%20during%20and%20after%20the%20wildfires%20on%20Maui%20and%20Hawaii%20islands%20this%20week.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20Friday%2C%20Maui%20County%20officials%20revised%20the%20death%20count%20to%2080%20and%20Governor%20Josh%20Green%20warned%20that%20the%20number%20of%20fatalities%20was%20sure%20to%20rise%20further.%20Over%201%2C400%20people%20were%20in%20emergency%20evacuation%20shelters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20underestimated%20the%20lethality%2C%20the%20quickness%20of%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20Hawaii%20Congresswoman%20Jill%20Tokuda%20told%20CNN%20on%20Saturday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJeremy%20Greenberg%2C%20FEMA's%20director%20of%20operations%20and%20for%20years%20a%20volunteer%20fireman%20himself%2C%20said%20the%20recent%20blaze%20was%20of%20a%20type%20%26quot%3Bextraordinarily%20difficult%26quot%3B%20to%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20talk%20about%20these%20types%20of%20fires%20moving%20as%20quickly%20as%20the%20length%20of%20a%20football%20field%20in%2020%20seconds%20or%20less%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20MSNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaui%20suffered%20numerous%20power%20outages%20during%20the%20crisis%2C%20preventing%20many%20residents%20from%20receiving%20emergency%20alerts%20on%20their%20cellphones%20--%20something%2C%20Tokuda%20said%2C%20officials%20should%20have%20prepared%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20got%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20we%20do%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreenberg%20said%20FEMA%20and%20its%20allied%20agenc