C%20the%20New%20York%20Post%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F08%2F11%2Fmy-great-dane-takes-up-two-seats-on-a-plane-i-dont-care-i-need-her%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGabriel%20Bogner%20paid%20for%20a%20row%20of%20seats%20on%20the%20flight%20for%20himself%20and%20his%20dog%2C%20Darwin%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20took%20the%20140-pound%20Great%20Dane%20on%20the%20flight%20when%20he%20moved%20from%20LA%20to%20Brooklyn%20after%20he%20said%20she%20was%20deemed%20too%20big%20to%20fit%20into%20the%20airline's%20cargo%20crate%2C%20per%20the%20outlet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40gibbon1215%2Fvideo%2F7238759922782063915%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%20that's%20received%20over%20%C2%A017.9%20million%20views%20and%202.9%20million%20likes%20since%20it%20was%20posted%20at%20the%20end%20of%20May%2C%20Darwin%20is%20seen%20sprawled%20on%20her%20back%20in%20the%20airport%20before%20meeting%20the%20flight's%20pilots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20were%20absolutely%20gobsmacked%20and%20shocked%2C%20but%20everyone%20was%20so%20excited%20to%20see%20her.%20I've%20never%20seen%20so%20many%20people%20smiling%20at%20an%20airport%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20South%20West%20News%20Service%2C%20per%20The%20Post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20it%20must%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Ba%20shocker%26quot%3B%20for%20people%20to%20see%20a%20%26quot%3Bliteral%20horse%20coming%20toward%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20The%20Post%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20five-hour%20flight%2C%20the%20TikTok%20also%20shows%20Darwin%20lounging%20across%20two%20seats%20next%20to%20her%20owner%20and%20sticking%20her%20head%20over%20the%20seats%20in%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBogner%20said%20airline%20staff%20joked%20that%20Darwin%20had%20got%20an%20upgrade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3