%20communal%20clashes%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20government%20informed%20the%20court%20that%20it%20was%20not%20a%20case%20of%20%E2%80%9Cethnic%20cleansing%E2%80%9D%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20earlier%20comment%20on%20the%20demolitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%2C%20on%20August%207%2C%20had%20stayed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnuh-demolitions-residents-due-process-damages%5C%22%3Edemolition%20drive%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Nuh%2C%20taking%20suo%20moto%20cognisance%20of%20the%20matter.%20It%20had%20ordered%20the%20Haryana%20government%20to%20halt%20demolitions%20until%20further%20orders.%20In%20a%20matter%20of%20five%20days%2C%20authorities%20said%20more%20than%20750%20%E2%80%9Cillegally%20constructed%E2%80%9D%20properties%20were%20demolished%2C%20amidst%20allegations%20of%20authorities%20targeting%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fdemolition-drive-haryana-dismisses-ethnic-cleansing-charge%2Farticle67184819.ece%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20additional%20advocate-general%20Deepak%20Sabharwal%20told%20the%20court%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20demolition%20in%20Nuh%20and%20Gurugram%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20following%20all%20due%20procedures%20established%20under%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20so%20far%20has%20been%20heard%20by%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Arun%20Palli%20and%20Jagmohan%20Bansal.%20It%20will%20now%20be%20placed%20before%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20high%20court%2C%20who%20will%20hear%20the%20matter%20on%20August%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Nuh%20district%20superintendent%20of%20police%20(SP)%2C%20Narendra%20Bijarniya%2C%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fnuh-sp-denies-any-long-term-planning-behind-nuh-violence%2Farticle67184711.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20there%20was%20no%20%E2%80%9Clong-term%E2%80%9D%20planning%20behind%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20blamed%20the%20violence%20on%20a%20combination%20of%20things%2C%20including%20%E2%80%9Csimmering%20discontent%20in%20the%20Mewat%20region%20over%20inaction%20in%20the%20Junaid%20and%20Nasir%20murder%20case%20in%20February%20this%20year%2C%20political%20rhetoric%2C%20and%20a%20few%20aggressive%20elements%20sneaking%20into%20the%20procession%E2%80%9D.%20He%20also%20said%20provocative%20social%20media%20posts%20from%20both%20sides%20also%20resulted%20in%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20went%20on%20to%20add%20that%C2%A0around%2050%20young%20men%20from%20villages%20in%20Rajasthan%20bordering%20Haryana%20came%20to%20stay%20at%20a%20hotel%20in%20Badkali%20and%20stones%20were%20piled%20up%20as%20part%20of%20the%20conspiracy%20to%20attack%20the%20procession.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CThe%20investigation%20so%20far%20suggests%20that%20one%20to%20two%20days%20of%20planning%20had%20gone%20into%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20393%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%20and%20160%20first%20information%20reports%20(FIRs)%20have%20been%20registered%20in%20connection%20with%20Nuh%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691846901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F08154007%2Fimage2.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fnuh-demolitions-haryana-govt-tells-hc-that-due-process-was-followed-denies-ethnic-cleansing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Authorities%20demolished%20more%20than%20750%20%26quot%3Billegally%20constructed%26quot%3B%20properties%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20violence%20in%20Nuh%2C%20amidst%20allegations%20of%20authorities%20targeting%20Muslims.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fnuh-demolitions-harya