.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsenator-anwaar-ul-haq-kakar-to-be-pakistan-s-caretaker-prime-minister-123081200339_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Senator%20Anwaar-ul-Haq%20Kakar%20was%20on%20Saturday%20picked%20as%20Pakistan's%20caretaker%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20govern%20the%20cash-strapped%20country%20and%20oversee%20general%20elections%20later%20this%20year.%5CnOutgoing%20Prime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20and%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20Raja%20...%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsenator-anwaar-ul-haq-kakar-to-be-pakistan-s-caretaker-prime-minister-123081200339_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fworld-news%2Fsenator-anwaar-ul-haq-kakar-to-be-pakistan-s-caretaker-prime-minister-123081200339_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fworld-news%2Fsenator-anwaar-ul-haq-kakar-to-be-pakistan-s-caretaker-prime-minister-123081200339_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MP%3A%20Muslims%20Who%20Protested%20Anti-Islam%20Social%20Media%20Post%20to%20Face%20NSA%20for%20'Controversial'%20Slogans%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Fmp-minister-pti.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20home%20minister%20Narottam%20Mishra%20has%20said%20penal%20action%20under%20the%20stringent%20National%20Security%20Act%20(NSA)%20would%20be%20taken%20against%20some%20people%20in%20Ratlam%20district%20of%20the%20state%20who%20allegedly%20raised%20slogans%20calling%20for%20the%20beheading%20of%20a%20person%20who%20had%20posted%20an%20objectionable%20social%20media%20post%20on%20Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20night%20of%20August%209%2C%20a%20large%20group%20of%20people%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%20gathered%20in%20large%20numbers%20outside%20a%20police%20outpost%20under%20Deen%20Dayal%20Nagar%20police%20station%20in%20Ratlam%20demanding%20action%20against%20a%20person%20who%20had%20posted%20objectionable%20content%20against%20their%20faith%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMembers%20of%20a%20community%20(Muslims)%20were%20angered%20by%20a%20social%20media%20post%20and%20gathered%20at%20the%20police%20outpost%20demanding%20that%20an%20FIR%20be%20lodged%20in%20the%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ratlam%20Additional%20SP%20Rajesh%20Khaka%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20later%20reported%20that%20some%20of%20the%20protestors%20outside%20the%20police%20outpost%20had%20allegedly%20raised%20a%20controversial%20slogan%20of%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Esar%20tan%20se%20juda%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20often%20evoked%20by%20fundamentalist%20Muslims%20in%20blasphemy%20cases.%20Videos%20of%20the%20alleged%20slogans%20were%20widely%20shared%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20access%20the%20objectionable%20post%20nor%20can%20it%20independently%20verify%20the%20veracity%20of%20the%20videos%20with%20the%20controversial%20slogans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20query%20by%20a%20reporter%2C%20home%20minister%20Mishra%20said%20on%20Friday%2C%20August%2011%2C%20that%20those%20accused%20of%20raising%20the%20slogans%20would%20be%20arrested%20and%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20against%20them%20under%20the%20NSA.%20An%20FIR%20was%20already%20lodged%20and%20the%20accused%20have%20been%20identified%2C%20he%20added%2C%20without%20providing%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%20me%20make%20this%20clear%2C%20this%20is%20not%20Rajasthan%20nor%20is%20there%20a%20Congress%20government%20here.%20This%20is%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20And%20those%20raising%20such%20%3Cem%3Eatanki%3C%2Fem%3E%20(terrorist)%20slogans%20will%20realise%20in%2024%20hours%E2%80%A6be%20careful%20otherwise%2C%20they%20will%20not%20understand%20what%20all%20will%20be%3Cem%3E%20juda%3C%2Fem%3E%20(pulled%20apart)%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mishra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERatlam%20Additional%20SP%20late%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20a%20case%20under%20Section%20295%20A%20(deliberate%20and%20malicious%20acts%20intended%20to%20outrage%20religious%20feelings)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20was%20lodged%20against%20the%20person%20who%20posted%20the%20objectionable%20post%20and%20promised%20to%20take%20strict%20action%20against%20the%20culprit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Kumar%20Lodha%2C%20Ratlam%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20on%20August%2011%20said%20action%20had%20been%20taken%20against%20the%20person%20who%20posted%20the%20objectionable%20post%20which%20had%20triggered%20a%20protest%20by%20the%20local%20Muslims.%20However%2C%20police%20are%20yet%20to%20reveal%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20and%20whether%20or%20not%20the%20accused%20was%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELodha%20also%20said%20that%20a%20case%20under%20Section%20188%20of%20the%20IPC%20%E2%80%93%20which%20deals%20with%20deliberate%20disobedience%20of%20an%20order%20by%20a%20public%20servant%20%E2%80%93%20had%20also%20been%20lodged%20against%20the%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20gathering%E2%80%9D%20outside%20the%20police%20outpost.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20some%20people%20instigated%20others%20to%20join%20the%20crowd%20and%20gather%20outside%20the%20police%20outpost.%20The%20said%20persons%20would%20be%20identified%20through%20CCTV%20footage%20and%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20them%2C%20Lodha%20said%20in%20a%20video%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20officer%20also%20appealed%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Ratlam%20to%20stop%20posting%20objectionable%20and%20provocative%20content%20on%20social%20media.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20not%20spare%20anyone%20who%20spoils%20the%20social%20harmony%20of%20the%20town%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691844182000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F