ormer%C2%A0President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fjair-bolsonaro%2Ft-48797570%5C%22%3EJair%20Bolsonaro%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20people%20close%20to%20him%2C%20that%20he%20had%20received%20as%20a%20gift%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia%20while%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sale%20of%20the%20luxury%20watches%20amounted%20to%C2%A0nearly%20%2470%2C000%20(%E2%82%AC63%2C847)%20which%20was%20allegedly%20kept%20by%20the%20former%20president%20as%20cash%2C%20violating%20laws%20that%20prohibit%20officials%20from%20keeping%20expensive%20gifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Federal%20Police%20officer%20told%20the%20Associated%20Press%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20that%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20access%20the%20personal%20banking%20and%20financial%20information%20of%20Bolsonaro%2C%20and%C2%A0had%20sought%20help%20from%20the%20FBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20had%20earlier%20carried%20out%20raids%20at%20the%20residences%20of%20Bolsonaro%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20Frederick%20Wassef%2C%20and%20the%20family%20of%20his%20aide%20Mauro%20Cid%20who%20is%20currently%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20search%20operations%20were%20executed%20based%20on%20a%20warrant%20issued%20by%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Alexandre%20de%20Moraes.%20Police%20said%20they%20believed%20Bolsonaro%E2%80%99s%20aides%20had%C2%A0used%20government%20resources%20for%20%E2%80%9Cillicit%20enrichment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20did%20Bolsonaro%20say%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrazil%20requires%20its%20citizens%20arriving%20by%20plane%20from%20abroad%20to%20declare%20goods%20worth%20more%20than%20%241%2C000%C2%A0(%E2%82%AC912).%20For%20any%20amount%20above%20that%2C%C2%A0a%20tax%20equal%20to%2050%25%20of%20their%20value%20has%20to%20be%20paid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20jewelry%20was%20a%20gift%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia%20to%20Brazil%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20exempt%20from%20tax%2C%20but%20not%20Bolsonaro%E2%80%99s%20to%20keep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20amounts%20obtained%20from%20these%20sales%20were%20transformed%20into%20cash%20and%20then%20became%20personal%20assets%20of%20the%20former%20president%20through%20middle%20people%20and%20without%20entering%20the%20formal%20banking%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20Federal%20Police%20said%2C%20according%20to%20an%20order%20issued%20by%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Alexandre%20de%20Moraes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeyond%20allowing%20an%20inadmissible%20enrichment%20of%20the%20President%20of%20the%20Republic%E2%80%A6%20it%20is%20possible%20that%20the%20Brazilian%20head%20of%20state%20was%20co-opted%20by%20foreign%20nations%20through%20these%20assets%2C%E2%80%9D%20investigators%20added%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBolsonaro%E2%80%99s%20lawyers%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20%E2%80%9CPresident%20Bolsonaro%20has%20never%20embezzled%20or%20misplaced%20any%20public%20assets%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20he%20would%20allow%20the%20judiciary%20to%20access%C2%A0his%20banking%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20also%20stated%20the%20police%20believe%20the%20strategy%20of%20the%20suspects%20was%20%E2%80%9Chiding%20the%20origin%2C%20location%20and%20ownership%20of%20these%20amounts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBolsonaro%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20legal%20troubles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20investigation%2C%20Bolsonaro%E2%80%99s%20aide%20Cid%20allegedly%20sold%20a%20Rolex%20watch%20and%20a%20Patek%20Philippe%20watch%20to%20a%20US%20store.%20This%20was%20given%20as%20a%20gift%20by%20the%20government%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia%20in%202019%20for%20a%20total%20of%20%2468%2C000.%20The%20money%20was%20allegedly%20transferred%20to%20the%20bank%20account%20of%20Cid%E2%80%99s%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202023%2C%20Federal%20Police%20asked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fbrazil-bolsonaro-returns-after-self-imposed-florida-exile%2Fa-65179174%5C%22%3EBolsonaro%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20return%20two%20sets%20of%20jewel