3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20Bill%2C%20which%20gives%20the%20Union%20government%20control%20over%20the%20postings%20and%20transfers%20of%20bureaucrats%20in%20Delhi%2C%20was%20opposed%20by%20the%20INDIA%20coalition%20of%20opposition%20parties.%20It%20will%20replace%20the%20ordinance%20promulgated%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20May%20this%20year%20to%20create%20the%20National%20Capital%20Civil%20Service%20Authority%20to%20administer%20the%20transfer%20and%20posting%20of%20bureaucrats%20serving%20the%20Delhi%20government.%20The%20ordinance%20itself%20was%20passed%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20said%20the%20national%20capital%20territory%20government%20has%20legislative%20power%20over%20bureaucrats%20in%20all%20departments%20other%20than%20public%20order%2C%20police%20and%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%20has%20been%20roundly%20criticised%20by%20activists%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwill-the-data-protection-law-empower-the-public%5C%22%3Esay%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20will%20enable%20surveillance%2C%20will%20not%20stop%20personal%20data%20collection%20by%20Big%20Tech%20companies%2C%20reduce%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20RTI%20law%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fdigital-personal-data-protection-bill-adverse-impact-press-freedom-editors-guild%5C%22%3Ehinder%20press%20freedom%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20two%20other%20Bills%20that%20have%20been%20signed%20by%20the%20president%2C%20the%20Registration%20of%20Births%20and%20Deaths%20(Amendment)%20Act%20will%20make%20digital%20birth%20certificates%20the%20only%20conclusive%20age%20proof.%20This%20law%20has%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fregistration-of-births-deaths-aadhaar-voter-id%5C%22%3Esparked%20concerns%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20surveillance%20and%20that%20it%20may%20impede%20the%20registration%20of%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jan%20Vishwas%20(Amendm