20BJP-RSS%20Intent%20on%20Polarisation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F25145206%2Fnot-in-my-name_PTI.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAmongst%20social%20groups%20that%20are%20being%20singled%20out%20for%20discrimination%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20ways%20are%20Muslims%2C%20who%20are%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20loss%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20Personal%20security%20and%20dignity%20score%20the%20worst.%20Yet%20the%20scale%20of%20pain%20and%20indignity%20being%20inflicted%20on%20innocent%20people%20in%20Manipur%20tells%20us%20that%20worse%20can%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForbearance%20and%20fortitude%20have%20been%20conspicuous%20in%20the%20reaction%20of%20ordinary%20Muslims%2C%C2%A0but%20hopefully%20as%20a%20sensible%20survival%20crisis%20strategy%20and%20not%20defeat%20or%20surrender%20to%20circumstances%20beyond%20control.%20The%20public%20strategy%20to%20react%20on%20behalf%20of%20all%20vulnerable%20victims%20rather%20than%20identified%20Muslims%20hopefully%20works%20to%20underscore%20the%20demand%20for%20relief%20without%20causing%20further%20hostility.%20But%20there%20remains%20a%20constant%20danger%20of%20ordinary%20folk%20losing%20faith%20in%20persons%20from%20whom%20clear%20advocacy%20is%20expected.%20Self-conscious%20silence%20%E2%80%93%20no%20matter%20how%20strategic%20%E2%80%93%20can%20be%20demoralising%20for%20the%20intended%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20there%20are%20innumerable%20non-Muslims%20who%20conspicuously%20speak%20their%20minds.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fharyana-at-least-1-killed-5-injured-as-clashes-breakout-during-rally-by-hindutva-outfits-in-nuh%5C%22%3EMewat%20mayhem%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20latest%20example.%20Hindu%20voices%20of%20sanity%20and%20secularism%20have%20kept%20the%20faith%20alive%20in%20our%20common%20humanity.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnuh-viol