nce%20or%20communal%20hostility%20in%20the%20past%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWay%20forward%20for%20the%20Muslims%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20larger%20picture%2C%20the%20red%20line%20has%20to%20be%20firmly%20drawn%20to%20curtail%20the%20erosion%20of%20values%20in%20the%20public%20space.%20Who%20else%20can%20do%20that%20but%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3F%20It%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20keep%20unwholesome%20proclivities%20in%20check%20through%20periodic%20orders%2C%20but%20some%20of%20its%20interim%20decisions%20such%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-greenlights-asi-gyanvapi-survey%23%3A~%3Atext%3Dlaw-%2CSC%2520Upholds%2520ASI%2520Survey%2520of%2520Gyanvapi%2520Premises%252C%2520Tells%2520Authorities%2520to%2C600%252Dyear%252Dold%2520structure.%5C%22%3Esurvey%20of%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20be%20encouraging%20people%20in%20unimagined%20ways.%20Of%20course%2C%20it%20is%20a%20tough%20job%20to%20keep%20all%20parties%20to%20litigation%20satisfied%20with%20fairness%20and%20natural%20justice.%20Yet%2C%20it%20might%20not%20be%20ultimately%20rewarding%20for%20the%20country%20to%20be%20encouraged%20to%20believe%20that%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20places%20of%20worship%2C%20the%20status%20quo%20of%20decades%20and%20centuries%20might%20be%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fayodhya-verdict-supreme-court-judgment%5C%22%3EAyodhya%20judgment%3C%2Fa%3E%20outcome%20has%20been%20accepted%20by%20all%20parties%20although%20many%20people%20continue%20to%20find%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-ayodhya-verdict-possession%5C%22%3Efault%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20legal%20reasoning.%20Be%20that%20as%20it%20may%2C%20even%20as%20it%20stands%2C%20it%20does%20not%20permit%20fresh%20challenges%20elsewhere%20having%20been%20decided%20strictly%20on%20principles%20of%20adverse%20possession%20and%20limitation.%20To%20keep%20the%20pot%20boiling%2C%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20with%20the%20passage%20of%20time%2C%20a%20negotiated%20settlement%20might%20be%20possible%20is%20patently%20contrary%20to%20the%20lessons%20of%20recent%20history.%20Some%20necessary%20accommodation%20to%20address%20the%20sense%20of%20disquiet%20%E2%80%93%20legitimate%20or%20otherwise%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20majority%20makes%20sense%2C%20but%20continuing%20down%20that%20path%20to%20rewrite%20history%20will%20be%20disastrous%20for%20the%20idea%20of%20India%20%E2%80%93%20that%20we%20the%20people%2C%20captured%20in%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderstandably%2C%20there%20is%20talk%20amongst%20minority%20citizens%20about%20what%20short-term%20and%20long-term%20communication%20strategies%20to%20adopt%20for%20a%20working%20relationship%20with%20the%20government%20and%20the%20majority%20they%20claim%20to%20represent.%20Periodically%20some%20people%20have%20taken%20the%20initiative%20to%20join%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmuslim-intellectuals-mohan-bhagwat-dialogue-or-monologues%5C%22%3Edialogue%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20high%20functionaries%20of%20the%20government%20and%20leadership%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20with%20uncertain%20results%20beyond%20photo%20ops%20and%20well-meaning%20press%20statements.%20Others%20have%20gone%20further%20to%20secure%20membership%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20have%20even%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fonly-one-party-wins-when-indian-muslims-defend-the-bjp%5C%22%3Enominated%20to%20the%20Upper%20House%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmuslims-must-dialogue-with-all-indians-except-those-who-dream-of-their-disenfranchisement%5C%22%3EMuslims%20Must%20Dialogue%20with%20All%20Indians%2C%20Except%20Those%20Who%20Dream%20of%20Their%20Disenfranchisement%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20adds%20to%20the%20support%20the%20BJP%20establishment%20has%20had%20for%20some%20time%20from%20conspicuous%20political%20persons%2C%20as%20indeed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Farif-mohammad-khan-kerala-governor%5C%22%3Eincumbent%20governor%20of%20Kerala%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Muslim%20institutions%20whose%20heads%20have%20shown%20implicit%20or%20explicit%20support%20for%20the%20BJP%20have%20added%20precious%20little%20to%20a%20larger%20conversation%20as%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20institutional%20following%20are%20cynical%20about%20such%20efforts%2C%20dismissing%20them%20as%20opportunist%20overtures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20minority%20universities%20are%20willy-nilly%20showing%20compliance%20to%20the%20wishes%20of%20political%20bosses.%20It%20might%20be%20too%20early%20to%20estimate%20the%20cost%20of%20all%20this%20in%20terms%20of%20quality%20and%20integrity%20of%20thinking%20of%20faculty%20and%20student%20body.%20Meanwhile%2C%20protests%20have%20become%20difficult%2C%20if%20not%20impossible%2C%20as%20many%20students%20discovered%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20CAA-NRC%20demonstrations%20in%20different%20cities%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20cannot%20reject%20dialogue%20entirely%20and%20hope%20that%20both%20sides%20engage%20in%20it%20with%20honest%20intentions%20and%20sincerity.%20Better%20understanding%20of%20each%20other%20is%20the%20purpose%20of%20dialogue%20and%20that%20might%20reduce%20suspicions%20and%20misplaced%20fear.%20But%20for%20successful%20inter-faith%20dialogue%2C%20an%20element%20of%20internal%20dialogue%20in%20the%20community%20might%20be%20essential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20cannot%20forget%20that%20our%20present%20condition%20is%20largely%20caused%20by%20the%20absence%20of%20internal%20dialogue%20ensured%20by%20the%20political%20ambitions%20of%20individuals%20and%20political%20outfits.%20Of%20course%2C%20before%20venturing%20to%20resume%20dialogue%20within%20the%20community%2C%20we%20may%20first%20need%20to%20reassess%20the%20performance%20of%20those%20we%20trusted%20over%20the%20months%20and%20years%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhere%20have%20we%20been%20let%20down%3F%20Who%20has%20failed%20us%20and%20why%3F%20Unless%20we%20get%20the%20correct%20prognosis%20for%20our%20condition%2C%20we%20cannot%20take%20the%20steps%20that%20will%20provide%20a%20cure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Fauthor%2FSalman-Khurshid%5C%22%3ESalman%20Khurshid%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Ci%3Emember%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20a%20senior%20advocate%2C%20a%20former%20MP%2C%20and%20a%20former%20Union%20minister%20of%20Law%20and%20Minority%20Affairs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691827195000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F25145206%2Fnot-in-my-name_PTI.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fserious-challenges-muslim-community-bjp-rss-polarisation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Seeking%20to%20appease%20the%20BJP%20via%20'dialogue'%20by%20certain%20Muslim%20'representatives'%20may%20not%20be%20the%20answer.%20The%20community%20needs%20to%20work%20towards%20a%20correct%20prognosis%20of%20its%20condition%2C%20before%20it%20decides%20on%20steps%20that%20will%20provide%20a%20cure.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fserious-challenges-muslim-community-bjp-rss-polarisation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22U2%E2%80%99s%20Bono%20Wows%20Crowd%2C%20Serenades%20Sarajevo%20in%20Surprise%20Appearance%20at%20Bosnian%20Film%20Festival%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691826735000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FBono-in-Sarajevo.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D123