rendra%20Modi%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20August%2010%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20can%20possibly%20have%20made%20the%20prime%20minister%20court%20this%20indignity%3F%20Surely%2C%20he%20knows%20that%20showing%20empathy%20with%20the%20poor%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20win%20their%20hearts%3F%20He%20has%20only%20to%20remember%20how%20Mrs%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20instant%20concern%20for%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20poor%20made%20her%20spectacular%20political%20comeback%20in%201980%20possible.%20The%20pivotal%20event%20then%20was%20the%20massacre%20of%20Dalits%20that%20took%20place%20in%201977%20in%20Belchi%2C%20a%20village%20in%20Bihar%2C%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20upper%20caste%20landowners.%20Despite%20being%20on%20trial%20before%20the%20Shah%20Commission%20for%20the%20excesses%20committed%20during%20the%20Emergency%2C%20she%20flew%20to%20Bihar%20and%20rode%20on%20an%20elephant%20to%20reach%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20the%20quality%20of%20spontaneous%20sympathy%20that%20gave%20her%20a%20near-divine%20status%20among%20the%20poor.%20Modi%20is%20too%20good%20a%20politician%20not%20to%20know%20the%20value%20of%20such%20gestures%2C%20so%20his%20profound%20silence%20has%20to%20be%20traced%20to%20other%2C%20more%20pressing%20concerns.%20The%20only%20one%20that%20springs%20to%20mind%20is%20his%20growing%20fear%20that%2C%20with%20opposition%20unity%20solidifying%20from%20month%20to%20month%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20in%20danger%20of%20losing%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20So%20he%20has%20gone%20back%20to%20the%20one%20antidote%20with%20which%20he%20is%20familiar%2C%20and%20which%20worked%20unfailingly%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20This%20is%20stirring%20up%20hatred%20of%20Muslims%20and%20other%20minorities%20in%20the%20Hindu%20majority.%20He%20did%20not%20plan%20the%20Manipur%20violence%2C%20but%20these%20played%20into%20his%20hands%20just%20as%20the%20Pulwama%20attack%20had%20done%20