th.%20He%20also%20called%20a%20conclave%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20coalition%20partners%20and%20set%20up%20a%20National%20Coordination%20Committee%20headed%20by%20George%20Fernandes%20as%20a%20counterweight%20to%20the%20RSS%20within%20his%20government.%20That%20balancing%20act%20gave%20India%20one%20of%20the%20best%20governments%20it%20has%20had%20since%20Independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Gujarat%20riots%20began%20on%20February%2028%2C%202002%2C%20after%20repeatedly%20failing%20to%20contact%20Modi%20on%20the%20phone%2C%20Vajpayee%20sent%20defence%20minister%20Fernandes%20to%20Ahmedabad%20to%20call%20in%20the%20army%20to%20end%20the%20violence.%20When%20he%20visited%20Ahmedabad%20a%20month%20later%2C%20he%20openly%20criticised%20Modi%20at%20the%20Shahpur%20refugee%20camp%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fvajpayee-wants-immediate-end-to-violence%2Farticleshow%2F5866129.cms%3F%5C%22%3Estating%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EMain%20yahan%20lashe%20ginane%20nahi%20aaya%20hoon%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%3Cem%3EAman%20kayam%20rakhna%20rajneetik%20neta%20aur%20adhikariyon%20ka%20zimmedari%20hai.%3C%2Fem%3E%20(I%20have%20not%20come%20here%20to%20count%20the%20corpses.%20It%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20political%20leaders%20and%20officials%20to%20maintain%20peace.)%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F09182736%2FAtlaji_addressing_political_rally_with_kaushal_ji_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F09182736%2FAtlaji_addressing_political_rally_with_kaushal_ji_.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F09182736%2FAtlaji_addressing_political_rally_with_kaushal_ji_-300x174.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F09182736%2FAtlaji_addressing_political_rally_with_kaushal_ji_-1024x595.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-652349%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22697%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAtal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee.%20Photo%3A%20KUNALJ73%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompare%20this%20with%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20steadfast%20refusal%20to%20condemn%2C%20and%20his%20tacit%20legitimisation%20through%20silence%2C%20of%20the%20lynching%20of%20more%20than%2050%20Muslims%20and%20Dalits%20by%20self-appointed%20%3Cem%3Egau%20rakshaks%20%3C%2Fem%3E(cow%20vigilantes)%2C%20his%20three-month%20long%20silence%20as%20Manipur%20has%20burned%2C%20and%20now%20his%20calculated%20silence%20over%20the%20outbreak%20of%20communal%20violence%20in%20Nuh%2C%20Gurgaon%20and%20Palwal.%20This%20makes%20the%20difference%20between%20a%20Hindu%20who%20understood%2C%20and%20wanted%20to%20foster%2C%20the%20essential%20tolerance%20of%20Hinduism%2C%20and%20a%20fake%20devotee%20who%20is%20abusing%20it%20to%20perpetuate%20his%20personal%20power%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20his%20country%20becomes%20starkly%20apparent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20write%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20has%20maintained%20his%20now-familiar%20enigmatic%20silence%20on%20the%20eruption%20of%20communal%20violence%20in%20Nuh%2C%20Gurgaon%20and%20Palwal%20for%20nine%20days.%20Through%20his%20silence%2C%20he%20has%20endorsed%20the%20Haryana%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20placing%20of%20the%20blame%20squarely%20upon%20Muslim%20youth%20in%20Nuh%20who%20allegedly%20attacked%20devotees%20who%20came%20to%20offer%20prayers%20at%20the%20Nalhar%20temple.%20This%20allegation%20has%20been%20so%20readily%20accepted%20that%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fin-the-shadow-of-the-millennium-city%2Farticle67158990.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520communal%2520clashes%2520spilled%2520over%2Cbuilt%2520with%2520bricks%2520and%2520mud).%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Csoon%20after%20they%20(the%20yatris)%20started%20the%20second%20leg%20of%20their%20journey%20from%20the%20Nalhar%20temple%20to%20a%20Radhakrishna%20temple%2060%20kms%20away%2C%20they%20were%20attacked%20by%20a%20mob%20.%20As%20stones%20were%20thrown%20at%20them%20and%20vehicles%20and%20shops%20set%20ablaze%20the%20devotees%20ran%20back%20to%20the%20temple%20in%20terror.%20They%20sat%20huddled%20inside%20for%20five%20hours%20as%20the%20mob%20surrounded%20the%20temple%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20description%20left%20out%20several%20key%20facts.%20The%20most%20important%20of%20these%20is%20that%20it%20was%20preceded%20by%20a%20full%20year%20of%20carefully%20planned%20provocation%20of%20an%20entirely%20peaceful%20Muslim%20population%20by%20the%20VHP%20and%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%2C%20to%20which%20the%20Haryana%20government%20consistently%20turned%20a%20blind%20eye.%20The%20first%20was%20that%20while%20the%20Nalhar%20temple%20was%20ancient%2C%20the%20pilgrimage%20to%20it%2C%20titled%20a%20Jalabhishekh%20Yatra%20(offering%20of%20holy%20water%20from%20the%20Ganges%20to%20Lord%20Shiva)%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Findia-news%2Fnuh-violence-fir-reveals-ordeal-people-locked-inside-temple-mob-haryana%2F3197878%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonly%20three%20years%20old%2C%20and%20had%20been%20launched%20by%20the%20VHP%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20express%20purpose%20of%20reclaiming%20Mahabharat-age%20temples%20from%20the%20Muslims.%20The%20article%20also%20did%20not%20mention%20that%20most%20of%20the%20pilgrims%20in%20the%20Jalabhishekh%20Yatra%20were%20not%20ordinary%20men%20and%20women%20of%20all%20ages%20but%20almost%20exclusively%20young%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnuh-temple-priest-refutes-haryana-home-ministers-claim-that-people-are-held-hostage%5C%22%3ENuh%20Temple%20Priest%20Refutes%20Haryana%20Home%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Claim%20That%20People%20Were%20%E2%80%98Held%20Hostage%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20was%20that%20the%20fracas%20in%20Nuh%20town%20was%20caused%20by%20a%20string%20of%20provocations%20that%20had%20begun%20a%20year%20or%20more%20before%20the%20violence%20occurred.%20The%20first%20provocation%20took%20place%20in%202022%20when%20a%20%3Cem%3Emazaar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20sufi%20shrine)%20was%20vandalised%2C%20but%20the%20elders%20of%20both%20communities%20contained%20the%20reaction.%20This%20year%2C%20however%2C%20saw%20a%20rapid%20fire%20string%20of%20further%20provocations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20a%20self%20styled%20gau%20rakshak%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fnuh-violence-monu-manesar-denies-involvement-in-communal-clashes-says-maman-khan-is-11690948108850.html%5C%22%3Enamed%20Monu%20Manesar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20is%20a%20Bajrang%20Dal%20activist%20on%20the%20run%20from%20the%20Rajasthan%20police%20for%20killing%20two%20Muslims%2C%20Nasir%20and%20Junaid%2C%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20posted%20a%20succession%20of%20inflammatory%20videos%20and%20promised%20that%20he%20would%20attend%20the%20Shobha%20Yatra%20at%20the%20Nalhar%20temple%20on%20Monday%20personally%2C%20to%20bathe%20the%20Shivling%20in%20Ganges%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F02150424%2FMonu-Manesar.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F02150424%2FMonu-Manesar.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F02150424%2FMonu-Manesar-300x274.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F02150424%2FMonu-Manesar-1024x936.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-666291%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221097%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMonu%20Manesar.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40MonuManesar.%20January%2021%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20another%20notorious%20Muslim%20baiter%20and%20self-advertised%20member%20of%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%2C%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%2C%20uploaded%20a%20series%20of%20venomous%20anti-Muslim%20videos%20on%20various%20channels%2C%20in%20one%20of%20which%20he%20claimed%20derisively%20that%20%E2%80%98Nuh%20was%20the%20Hindu%20community%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Esasural%3C%2Fem%3E%20(in-laws%E2%80%99%20house)%E2%80%99.%20No%20one%20failed%20to%20understand%20the%20insult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20agent%20provocateur%20who%20had%20also%20announced%20his%20intention%20to%20join%20the%20Yatra%20this%20year%20was%20yet%20another%20Bajrang%20Dal%20member%20who%20is%20known%20by%20his%20%3Cem%3Enom%20de%20guerre%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%98Rambhakt%20Gopal%E2%80%99.%20He%20gained%20notoriety%20in%202020%20by%20firing%20a%20revolver%20at%20protestors%20demonstrating%20against%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20in%20Shaheen%20Bagh%2C%20shouting%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EYeh%20lo%20azaadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Here%E2%80%99s%20your%20freedom)%E2%80%9D%20as%20he%20retreated%2C%20still%20holding%20his%20revolver%20up%2C%20into%20the%20protective%20ranks%20of%20a%20hundred%20Delhi%20policemen%20who%20did%20nothing%20to%20deter%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%20Nuh%20march%2C%20Gopal%20had%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-violence-mewat-hate-and-provocative-videos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euploaded%20two%20videos%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20first%20of%20armed%20persons%20in%20a%20jeep%20terrorising%20women%20and%20children%20in%20a%20Muslim%20village%2C%20and%20the%20second%2C%20captioned%20%E2%80%9CTaking%20away%20the%20cow%20smuggler%E2%80%9D%20was%20of%20young%20men%20dragging%20a%20Muslim%20into%20an%20SUV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20Monu%20Manesar%20nor%20Gopal%20turned%20up%20at%20Nuh%2C%20but%20the%20damage%20had%20been%20done%20and%20the%20town%20was%20seething%20with%20young%20men%20who%20were%20determined%20to%20take%20revenge.%20It%20was%20in%20these%20conditions%20that%2C%20after%20visiting%20the%20Nalhar%20temple%2C%20the%20Jalabhishekh%20Yatris%20decided%20to%20go%20through%20the%20centre%20of%20Nuh%20town%20to%20their%20second%20shrine%2C%20the%20Radhakrishna%20temple%20at%20Singar%20village%2C%2060%20km%20away.%20This%20made%20the%20resulting%20violence%20unavoidable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-violence-mewat-hate-and-provocative-videos%5C%22%3EHaryana%20Violence%3A%20How%20Provocative%20Videos%20and%20a%20Background%20of%20Hate%20Preceded%20the%20Nuh%20Riots%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20followed%20the%20now%20familiar%20BJP%20routine%20of%20blaming%20the%20victims%20for%20the%20atrocities%20they%20had%20suffered.%20By%20Friday%2C%20just%20four%20days%20after%20the%20riot%20in%20Nuh%2C%20the%20Haryana%20police%20force%20that%20had%20done%20absolutely%20nothing%20to%20prevent%20a%20well%20publicised%20riot%2C%20had%20arrested%20as%20many%20as%20141%20persons%20and%20registered%2055%20FIRs%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20violence.%20It%20has%20not%20given%20any%20data%20as%20to%20who%2C%20precisely%2C%20they%20have%20arrested.%20But%20it%20is%20safe%20to%20assume%20that%20j%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdelhi-police-affidavit-shows-muslims-bore-brunt-of-riots-silent-on-who-targeted-them-and-why%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eust%20as%20happened%20after%20the%20East%20Delhi%20riots%20three%20years%20ago%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhere%20despite%2040%20out%20of%2053%20persons%20killed%20being%20Muslims%20and%20most%20of%20the%20property%20destroyed%20being%20Muslim-owned%2C%20all%20but%20a%20handful%20of%20those%20arrested%20were%20also%20Muslims%20%E2%80%93%20most%20of%20those%20who%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20Nuh%20will%20also%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20there%20is%20data%20for%20already%20is%20the%20revenge%20that%20the%20police%20has%20taken%20upon%20the%20Muslims%20of%20Nuh.%20Almost%20all%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnuh-demolitions-residents-due-process-damages%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%20750%20homes%2C%20huts%2C%20shops%2C%20restaurants%20and%20cinema%20halls%20demolished%20by%20the%20Haryana%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20the%20riot%2C%20allegedly%20for%20suddenly%20discovered%20illegal%20construction%2C%20belong%20to%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20this%20tragedy%2C%20Modi%20has%20maintained%20his%20sphinx-like%20silence%20while%20his%20advisers%20worked%20out%20how%20to%20convert%20the%20resulting%20increase%20in%20Hindu-Muslim%20animosity%20into%20votes%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%202024.%20The%20first%20fruit%20of%20their%20cogitations%20has%20not%20taken%20long%20to%20ripen.%20On%20Wednesday%20August%209%2C%20a%20bare%2048%20hours%20after%20the%20Muslim%20property%20destruction%20drive%20began%2C%20the%20Haryana%20BJP%20chief%2C%20Om%20Prakash%20Dhankar%2C%20had%20the%20brazen-faced%20gall%20to%20accuse%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Aam%20Admi%20Party%20of%20having%20instigated%20the%20riots.%20He%20and%20his%20five-member%20delegation%20did%20this%20without%20even%20having%20visited%20Nuh%2C%20but%20after%20the%20police%20had%20prevented%20a%20Congress%20delegation%20from%20going%20to%20the%20town%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20an%20AAP%20delegation%20from%20doing%20so%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20causes%20of%20the%20communal%20conflagration%20in%20Manipur%20may%20have%20been%20local%2C%20and%20the%20violence%20unplanned%2C%20but%20the%20same%20cannot%20be%20said%20of%20the%20tragedy%20that%20has%20befallen%20the%20Meos%20of%20Nuh.%20Judging%20from%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20past%20actions%2C%20Nuh%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20followed%20by%20more%20communal%20violence%20triggered%20by%20the%20VHP%20and%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%2C%20but%20blamed%20upon%20local%20Muslims.%20As%20the%20BJP%20feels%20more%20threatened%20by%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20such%20provocations%20are%20set%20to%20multiply.%20India%20is%20therefore%20likely%20to%20go%20through%20the%20fires%20of%20hell%20before%20the%20next%20election.%20And%20if%20the%20BJP%20somehow%20comes%20out%20as%20the%20victor%2C%20it%20will%20almost%20certainly%20be%20the%20last%20proper%20general%20election%20this%20country%20will%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fprem-shankar-jha%5C%22%3EPrem%20Shankar%20Jha%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691810989000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11132501%2FH20230728135985.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felections-2024-india-most-dangerous-phase%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20violence%20in%20Nuh%2C%20Palwal%20and%20Gurgaon%20makes%20it%20clear%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20fallen%20back%20on%20the%20one%20antidote%20with%20which%20he%20is%20familiar%2C%20which%20worked%20unfailingly%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20This%20is%20the%20stirring%20up%20hatred%20of%20Muslims%20and%20other%20minorities%20in%20the%20Hindu%20majority.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22