%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fafzal-gunj-1691745063.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22724%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Afzal%20Gunj%20hospital%20was%20ravaged%20by%20the%20Musi%20floods%20in%201908%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fafzal-gunj-1691745063.jpg%20724w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fafzal-gunj-1691745063-300x221.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fafzal-gunj-1691745063-500x368.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fafzal-gunj-1691745063-150x110.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327027%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20international%20chloroform%20trials%20were%20held%20at%20the%20Afzal%20Gunj%20hospital.%20Image%3A%20The%20Deccan%20Archive%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20mid-19th%20century%2C%20medical%20education%20was%20picking%20up%20in%20Hyderabad%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20the%20Hyderabad%20Medical%20School.%20The%20land%20that%20houses%20the%20OGH%20campus%20today%20was%20earlier%20home%20to%20the%20Afzal%20Gunj%20Hospital%2C%20which%20was%20constructed%20in%201866%20and%20served%20as%20a%20teaching%20hospital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20at%20these%20two%20buildings%20that%20major%20medical%20breakthroughs%20were%20made.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20of%20malaria%20was%20made%20at%20the%20Hyderabad%20Medical%20School%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F272865%2Fhyderabad-fever-hospital-sir-ronald-ross-nobel-prize-malaria%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENobel%20laureate%20Sir%20Ronald%20Ross%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Afzal%20Gunj%20Hospital%20contributed%20to%20a%20major%20breakthrough%20in%20anesthesia.%20T