%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fvedha2-1691583886-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fvedha2-1691583886-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326815%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221120%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVedhapriya%20works%20in%20animal%20rescue%20and%20rehabilitation.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVedhapriya%20then%20decided%20to%20get%20proper%20training%20so%20that%20she%20could%20be%20better%20prepared%20for%20such%20situations.%20And%20who%20better%20to%20learn%20from%20than%20the%20Irulas%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tribe%20known%20for%20their%20snake-catching%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Irulas%20usually%20don%E2%80%99t%20teach%20this%20skill%20to%20others.%20You%20really%20need%20to%20win%20their%20trust.%C2%A0%20Since%20many%20younger%20Irulas%20are%20today%20pursuing%20education%2C%20they%20agreed%20to%20teach%20me.%20They%20guided%20me%20very%20well.%20I%20also%20did%20some%20professional%20courses%20in%20cobra%20rescue%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20still%20in%20college%2C%20she%20started%20volunteering%20with%20animal%20welfare%20organisations%2C%20the%20Central%20Zoo%20Authority%20of%20India%2C%20Blue%20Cross%2C%20and%20Besant%20Memorial%20Animal%20Dispensary.%20She%20also%20began%20working%20with%20the%20Western%20Ghat%20Wildlife%20Conservation%20Trust%20(WGWCT)%20where%20she%20continues%20to%20work%20as%20the%20chief%20co-ordinator%20for%20Chennai%20and%20the%20wildlife%20management%20specialist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20work%20closely%20with%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Forest%20Department%2C%20Vedhapriya%20is%20often%20called%20on%20for%20wildlife%20rescues.%20She%20says%20she%20has%20rescued%20more%20than%206%2C000%20snakes%20so%20far%20and%20recounts%20a%20rescue%20where%20a%20child%20was%20stuck%20inside%20a%20house%20with%20a%20snake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C