the%20moon%E2%80%99s%20surface%2C%20now%20to%20170%20km%20x%204313%20km.%20The%20next%20operation%20to%20further%20reduce%20the%20orbit%20is%20scheduled%20for%20August%209%2C%202023%2C%20between%2013%3A00%20and%2014%3A00%20Hrs%20IST%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20ISRO%20in%20a%20tweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20happens%20next%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChandrayaan%20has%20many%20critical%20events%20lined%20up%2C%20including%20earth-bound%20manoeuvres%2C%20insertion%20into%20the%20lunar%20orbit%2C%20separation%20of%20the%20lander%2C%20a%20set%20of%20deboost%20manoeuvres%20and%20a%20power%20descent%20phase%20for%20a%20soft%20landing%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20P%20Veeramuthuvel%2C%20project%20director%20of%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20spacecraft%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%20Mission%3A%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20orbit-raising%20maneuver%20(Earth-bound%20perigee%20firing)%20is%20performed%20successfully%20from%20ISTRAC%2FISRO%2C%20Bengaluru.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20spacecraft%20is%20expected%20to%20attain%20an%20orbit%20of%20127609%20km%20x%20236%20km.%20The%20achieved%20orbit%20will%20be%20confirmed%20after%20the%20observations.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20next%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FLYb4XBMaU3%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FLYb4XBMaU3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1683767962560512000%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2025%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%2C%20the%20spacecraft%20will%20go%20around%20the%20Moon%20to%20reduce%20its%20velocity%20in%20orbit%20and%20prepare%20for%20a%20soft%20landing%20on%20its%20surface.%20This%20orbiting%20will%20continue%20till%20Chandrayaan-3%20reaches%20a%20circular%20orbit%20of%20100%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20this%20is%20achieved%2C%20the%20lander%20and%20rover%20will%20descend%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F216483%2Fiisc-isro-moon-lunar-soil-simulant-space-brick-eco-friendly-homes-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurface%20of%20the%20Moon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20after%20being%20separated%20from%20the%20propulsion%20module.%20Chandrayaan-3%20is%20expected%20to%20reach%20the%20Moon%E2%80%99s%20surface%20by%2023%20August%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%20Mission%20Update%3A%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ELunar%20Orbit%20Insertion%20(LOI)%20maneuver%20was%20completed%20successfully%20today%20(August%2005%2C%202023).%20With%20this%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FChandrayaan3%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Chandrayaan3%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20successfully%20inserted%20into%20a%20Lunar%20orbit.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20next%20Lunar%20bound%20orbit%20maneuver%20is%20scheduled%20tomorrow%20(August%2006%2C%202023)%2C%20around%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FIC3MMDQMjU%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FIC3MMDQMjU%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20LVM3-M4%2FCHANDRAYAAN-3%20MISSION%20(%40chandrayaan_3)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchandrayaan_3%2Fstatus%2F1687831700452098048%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%205%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20successful%20completion%2C%20India%20will%20become%20the%20fourth%20country%20to%20achieve%20a%20lunar%20soft%20landing%20after%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20former%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20and%20China.%20Both%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20former%20Soviet%20Union%20failed%20many%20times%20before%20they%20successfully%20landed%20on%20the%20Moon.%20China%20was%20the%20only%20country%20to%20succeed%20in%20its%20first%20attempt%20with%20the%20Chang%E2%80%99e-3%20mission%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691408722000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D326455%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chandrayaan-3%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20lunar%20mission%20launched%20by%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%2C%20recently%20shared%20some%20stunning%20captures%20of%20the%20Moon.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20can%20expect%20next.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326455%2Fisro-chandrayaan-3-updates-first-pictures-of-the-moon-tweets-video%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BYOB%3A%20Friends%20Turn%207%20Lakh%20Glass%20Bottles%20into%20Quirky%20Art%20%26%20Home%20Decor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGayatri%20Fabian%2C%20based%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20affectionately%20labels%20herself%20as%20a%20hoarder%2C%20expressing%20her%20fondness%20for%20collecting%20items%2C%20particularly%20bottles.%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%20never%20have%20enough%20of%20them.%20I%20would%20go%20to%20scrap%20dealers%20and%20wander%20around%20looking%20for%20pretty-looking%20bottles%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20exclaims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20soon%20enough%20she%20found%20herself%20in%20a%20quirky%20predicament%20%E2%80%94%20her%20house%20had%20become%20a%20battleground%20of%20bottles!%20With%20a%20twinkle%20in%20her%20eye%2C%20she%20confesses%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20breathing%20space%20left.%20My%20poor%20kids%20teased%20me%20relentlessly%2C%20but%20hey%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20part%20with%20my%20precious%20collection.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELong%20ago%2C%20someone%20wise%20aptly%20expressed%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20person%E2%80%99s%20trash%20is%20another%20person%E2%80%99s%20treasure.%E2%80%9D%20Carrying%20the%20sentiment%20forward%2C%20Gayatri%20started%20to%20look%20for%20ways%20of%20using%20the%20mammoth%20amount%20of%20bottles%20in%20her%20storage%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20how%20she%20found%20%E2%80%98Kavi%20The%20Poetry-Art%20Project%E2%80%99%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286048%2Fbest-home-decor-influencers-interior-design-diy-recycle-ideas-tips-on-instagram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20venture%20that%20converts%20glass%20waste%20into%20pieces%20of%20home%20decor%20and%20utensils.%20Founded%20by%20Noida-based%20Madhuri%20Balodi%20and%20Amit%20Singh%2C%20the%20project%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F314356%2Fkerala-woman-upcycles-waste-glass-into-home-decor-vapasee-sustainable-venture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecollects%20glass%20bottles%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20ragpickers%20and%20customers%2C%20and%20converts%20them%20into%20serving%20sets%2C%20platters%2C%20drinking%20glasses%2C%20lamps%20and%20other%20such%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20never%20seen%20anyone%20do%20this%20before%2C%20so%20I%20spoke%20to%20them%2C%20I%20resonated%20with%20their%20ideology%20so%20much%20that%20I%20shipped%20six%20cartons%20full%20of%20bottles%20to%20them.%20They%20made%20me%20all%20sorts%20of%20things%20like%20planters%2C%20platters%2C%20vases%2C%20wine%20glasses%2C%20jars%20and%20lamps%20from%20these%20bottles%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20quality%20of%20the%20products%20is%20so%20good%2C%20I%20have%20gifted%20so%20many%20of%20those%20pieces%20to%20my%20friends%20and%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Gayatri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETesting%20the%20waters%20of%20sustainability%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EGreen%20Sutra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20India%20produces%20three%20million%20tonnes%20of%20glass%20waste%20every%20year.%20Out%20of%20this%2C%20only%2045%20percent%20is%20recycled%20while%20the%20rest%20ends%20up%20in%20landfills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-1-1691153646.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Co-founders%20of%20Kavi%20The%20Poetry%20Art%20Project%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-1-1691153646.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-1-1691153646-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-1-1691153646-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-1-1691153646-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-1-1691153646-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326394%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMadhuri%20Balodi%20and%20Amit%20Singh%2C%20co-founders%20of%20Kavi%20The%20Poetry-Art%20Project%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Madhuri%20Balodi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%2032-year-old%20Madhuri%2C%20sustainable%20living%20has%20always%20been%20a%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20realise%20how%20much%20harm%20we%20do%20to%20the%20environment%20with%20our%20daily%20activities.%20We%20might%20think%20that%20these%20glass%20bottles%20go%20to%20recycling%20but%20the%20ground%20reality%20is%20quite%20different.%20Most%20of%20them%20end%20up%20in%20landfills%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhuri%20met%20Amit%20while%20working%20in%20the%20media%20industry.%20%E2%80%9CAmit%20and%20I%20had%20a%20very%20similar%20outlook%20towards%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326200%2Fecosoul-home-india-boston-sustainable-plastic-free-kitchenware-cutlery-sugarcane-palm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elife%20and%20sustainability.%3C%2Fa%3E%20We%20would%20chat%20about%20how%20we%20could%20do%20something%20about%20it%20and%20ended%20up%20brainstorming%20ideas%20for%20hours.%20Being%20in%20the%20media%20industry%2C%20both%20of%20us%20were%20exposed%20first-hand%20to%20innovators%20around%20the%20world%20who%20were%20working%20in%20the%20sustainability%20field.%20We%20often%20heard%20topics%20like%20solar%20energy%2C%20upcycling%2C%20reusing%2C%20and%20recycling%20around%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLooking%20at%20so%20many%20people%20working%20towards%20sustainability%2C%20we%20thought%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Hum%20bhi%20kar%20sakte%20hai%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(we%20can%20do%20it%20too).%20So%20in%202013%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%2C%E2%80%9D%20Madhuri%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20started%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20sustainability%20and%20carbon%20footprint%20was%20not%20as%20popular%20as%20today.%20People%20were%20not%20as%20well-informed%20about%20the%20harm%20we%20do%20to%20the%20environment%2C%20and%20many%20did%20not%20care%20about%20what%20happened%20to%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvcsr95toXk%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvcsr95toXk%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fd